Example 
A--2--> B 
B--(-5)--> C 
A--1--> C
Let's use Dijkstras starting from A 
1. from A->B =2 
From A->C = 1
it thinks shortest to C  is a 1 
If we go A --> B ---> C then the total would be like 2 + ( -5) = -3 
